milestones.description: Hansie Cronje has become the top scorer for SA in ODIs with 1632 runs, going past Wessels's 1572
Hansie Cronje has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for SA breaking Gary Kirsten's record
Hansie Cronje and Eric Simons's 44-run partnership is SA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Peter Kirsten and McMillan
This is the highest match aggregate (503) involving teams Australia & South Africa in ODIs
